    "patch_code": "private boolean hasExceptionHandler(Node cfgNode) {\n  Statement statement = cfgNode.getFirstChild().castToStatement();\n  \n  while (statement != null && statement.isBlock()) {\n    for (int i = 0; i < statement.getNumChildren(); i++) {\n      Node child = statement.getChild(i).getLastChild();\n      \n      // If we found a try statement, then there must have been an exception handler.\n      if (child.getFirstChild().getFirstChild().getToken().getValue().equals(\"try\")) {\n        return true;\n      }\n    }\n    \n    // Get the next sibling.\n    statement = statement.getNextSibling().castToStatement();\n  }\n  \n  return false;\n}",
